# D. PROJECT CONTEXT (Key Facts)

- This is an iOS app called "Spotter" ‚Äî a real-time AI workout companion
- Built with Swift 5, SwiftUI, MediaPipe (via CocoaPods), targeting iOS 16+
- Uses MediaPipe PoseLandmarker (33 body points, 3D world coords), HandGestureDetector, FaceLandmarkerService
- Architecture: Camera ‚Üí Vision ‚Üí RepCounting ‚Üí Coaching ‚Üí UI
- Design system: "No-Fluff Noir" ‚Äî dark theme, single warm amber accent
- Two coach personalities: Bennett (supportive) and Fletcher (drill sergeant)
- The UniversalRepCounter is data-driven from ExerciseDefinition ‚Äî never write exercise-specific counter classes
- All angle calculations prefer 3D world coordinates over 2D
- The full project context is documented in `SPOTTER_CONTEXT_DOC.md` at project root
